[100.327741, "o", "\u001b[35m╭───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[35m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mStage 3/3: Evaluating tailored resume (Haiku judge)...\u001b[0m                            \u001b[35m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[35m╰───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[107.136814, "o", "\u001b[33m╭─\u001b[0m\u001b[33m─────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[33m Judge Verdict \u001b[0m\u001b[33m─────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[33m─╮\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;33mEmployability Score: 7/10\u001b[0m                                                         \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                   \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m This candidate is a strong match with exceptional depth in core AI/ML and medical \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m imaging domains. They demonstrate mastery of deep learning frameworks (PyTorch,   \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m TensorFlow), medical image analysis (segmentation, registration, 3D tracking),    \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m GPU programming, and have published research in computer vision. However, the PhD \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m is in Neuroscience rather than the preferred AI/ML/CS disciplines, and there are  \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m notable gaps in traditional deep reinforcement learning, DICOM standards, and     \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m TensorRT experience—all mentioned as preferred or plus qualifications.            \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33m╰───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[107.137051, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1mWeaknesses:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[107.137641, "o", "  \u001b[31m-\u001b[0m Limited traditional deep reinforcement learning \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mDRL\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m experience—candidate has \r\nbuilt LLM-based AI agents but not RL-based decision-making systems\r\n"]
[107.138448, "o", "  \u001b[31m-\u001b[0m No explicit DICOM standard experience mentioned, which is a desired qualification\r\nfor medical imaging work\r\n"]
[107.139115, "o", "  \u001b[31m-\u001b[0m No TensorRT experience mentioned, which is listed as a plus for optimization and \r\ndeployment\r\n"]
[107.139805, "o", "  \u001b[31m-\u001b[0m PhD in Neuroscience rather than AI/ML/CS/EE/CE/Bio-Engineering, though \r\ncomputational focus partially mitigates this\r\n"]
[107.14052, "o", "  \u001b[31m-\u001b[0m No mention of ultrasound image processing experience, though candidate has worked\r\nwith ultrasound imaging data\r\n"]
[107.14105, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1mSuggested Interview Prep Questions:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[107.142669, "o", "  \u001b[1;36m1\u001b[0m. Your resume shows strong experience with LLM-based AI agents and workflow \r\nautomation, but the role emphasizes deep reinforcement learning \u001b[1m(\u001b[0mDRL\u001b[1m)\u001b[0m frameworks for \r\nadaptive optimization. Can you describe your understanding of DRL and discuss whether\r\nyou've considered applying RL methods to medical imaging problems? What would be your\r\napproach to learning DRL if hired?\r\n"]
[107.143958, "o", "  \u001b[1;36m2\u001b[0m. Walk us through your experience with the 3D multi-object tracking and \r\nsegmentation project mentioned in your resume. Specifically, how did you handle \r\nreal-time processing requirements, and what GPU optimization techniques did you \r\nemploy? How would you approach deploying such a model in a clinical setting?\r\n"]
[107.144716, "o", "  \u001b[1;36m3\u001b[0m. You have clinical experience from your medical internship and work with \r\nelectronic health records. Can you describe a specific instance where your clinical \r\nknowledge directly informed your AI/ML work, and how you would apply that \r\ninterdisciplinary perspective to solving real-world problems for our surgical imaging\r\nplatform?\r\n"]
[107.14562, "o", "  \u001b[1;36m4\u001b[0m. The role requires familiarity with medical imaging standards and formats. While \r\nyour resume mentions MRI and ultrasound work, there's no mention of DICOM. How would \r\nyou approach learning DICOM standards, and what challenges do you anticipate in \r\nintegrating DICOM data into deep learning pipelines?\r\n"]
[107.146696, "o", "  \u001b[1;36m5\u001b[0m. Tell us about a time when you had to rapidly prototype and validate a new AI \r\nmodel under time constraints. How did you balance model complexity, validation rigor,\r\nand speed to market, and what would you do differently in a commercial medical device\r\ncontext versus research?\r\n"]
[107.15085, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2mFeedback saved to \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mreal_user/edda_research_scientist/edda_technology_ai_research_scientist_--_medical_ap\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2mplications/judge_feedback.txt\u001b[0m\r\n"]
